summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting the redevelopment proposal of Novalco Enterprises, Inc. to purchase and develop Parcel 40A in the Yesler-Atlantic Neighborhood Improvement Project (Wash. R-5) area; authorizing the Director of the Department of Housing and Human Services to execute, deliver and administer a contract and deed; designating the disposition of sales proceeds; and ratifying and confirming prior actions.
committee: Health, Human Services, Education and Libraries
